Question: Do you think the Federal Government should provide free healthcare?
Answer:
In a perfect world, the answer to this question would definitely be yes for me. However, it is a much more difficult question when financial concerns are considered. Even still, I think it is the responisibility of the government to make sure all of its citizens are protected, even if that is done at a basic level. Seeing as there are people in this country who do not make enough to afford healthcare, I think the government almost has to provide free healthcare.